    <stitle>AIR COMPRESSOR: BENDIX 2150 - INSPECTION - END COVERS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="inspect" graphiccount="0">
        <title>END COVERS</title>
        <para>Check for cracks, stripped oil port threads and external damage; and if noted, replace the end cover. lf
            the crankshaft main bearings are installed in the end cover, check for excessive wear and flat spots and
            replace the end cover if necessary.
        </para>
